gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 119, Wizards 109
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic win their fifth consecutive game as they defeat the Wizards, 119-109. Franz Wagner recorded 28 points and five rebounds for the Magic, while Paolo Banchero added 25 points, six rebounds and 10 assists in the victory. Jordan Poole tallied 26 points, four rebounds and five assists for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 37-26 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 9-53.
